<p>Understanding these categories is critical for knowing what's actually legal for you to buy and use.</p>

<h3>Prescription-Only Peptides</h3>

<p>These are FDA-approved drugs. You need a prescription from a licensed provider, and they must be dispensed by a licensed pharmacy.</p>

